    • href

      public final Base href(Object href)
      href attribute.

      Document base URL.

      The value can be of any of the following types: URI, URL, String. Strings must be valid URIs.

      URIs defined by UriResolver can be used for values.

      Parameters:
      href - The new value for this attribute. Typically a URL or String.
      Returns:
      This object.
